description:
This is the TrustedQSL project, which provides tools for digitally
signing Amateur Radio QSO records.


**Please Note**: This is an automatically updated package. If you find it is
out of date by more than a day or two, please contact the maintainer(s) and
let them know the package is no longer updating correctly.
summary:
Open source libraries and utilities to support using digital signatures for Amateur
radio QSL information
author: American Radio Relay League
